               <p>RICHARD WILKINSON. On the 13th of June, about half-past one o'clock at noon, I was in <placeName id="t18270712-120-crimeloc659">Chiswell-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18270712-120-crimeloc659" type="placeName" value="Chiswell-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18270712-120-crimeloc659" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270712-120-off657 t18270712-120-crimeloc659"></join>, and had my handkerchief stolen from my pocket. I did not see it taken; it was safe between eleven and twelve o'clock, when I left home - I did not see the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270712-120-person685">
                  JOHN 
                  BEE
