            . I am an officer. On the 13th of June I was at the corner of Bunhill-row, and saw the prisoner and three other boys together, following the prosecutor. I saw the prisoner take the handkerchief from the prosecutor's pocket, and roll it up. I ran up, took hold of him, and he threw it down.</p>
